Name: Little Chick
About the game: A difficult and boring game. Maybe you like or hate it. Control the chick's left and right balance through the mouse, and walk steadily through the long rope to the opposite mountain top. You may encounter bad weather on the way to make you unbalanced. Hope the chick is health. Any suggestion or feedback please contact us: greyame@163.com. Don't worry,be happy!
